              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " Neutron energy spectrum was divided into five energy",
                " bins with central energy 8.4, 15, 25, 42, 87 keV"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " .corrections were made for (1) backgrounds by room",
                "  returned neutrons, (2) fission events discriminated",
                "  in the pulse height spectrum, (3) self-absorption",
                "  in the fission sample, (4) fission events by the",
                "  neutrons by the chamber and the target"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Both 237Np and 235U samples were thin-layer electro-",
